data.description: Who is looking for country living with 25 acres that is in close proximity to the city? Look no further! 304 Big Pine is the answer to your private living! This modern farmhouse is an astonishing 4 bedroom 3 bath home with your own personal pond. You enter the front door by access of the southern style porch. Once you have entered you will be greeted with barn doors that open to an office or dining space. The gourmet kitchen is equipped with double wall ovens, an induction stove top, granite counter tops, an oversized island and custom cabinetry. The kitchen opens to the great room and oversized breakfast area. The great room has a stunning brick fireplace that is plumbed for gas logs or can be used as wood burning. There is also built in bookcases and cabinets, recessed lighting & double ceiling fans. There are 3 guest bedrooms on one side. One bathroom has entrance from hallway and one has a private entrance from the bedroom. The master bedroom features tray ceilings and there you enter you bath oasis through double doors. The master bath has a claw foot tub, beautiful, tiled shower that has a rain showerhead & multiple body jets. Through the master bath you can enter your large laundry room which features granite countertops & an abundance of cabinets. There is another bedroom off of the master that would be great for a nursery, office or workout room. There is wainscoting in the foyer and hallway to the garage. The 2 car side entry garage measures 25x25 with tall ceilings and 8ft garage doors. The land has a deep well and a private pond that would be perfect for swimming or fishing. The land is full of wildlife! There is a private entrance that is gated for residents only. You must have an agent to enter. The lot cannot be subdivided. Pre approval required for all appointments.
